# Keep the Docker build context small and free of host artifacts / secrets.
.git
**/node_modules
**/target
**/.next
**/dist
**/.turbo
**/.env
**/.env.*
# Exception: apps/webapp/.env.production is PUBLIC client config (api URL,
# public analytics keys) that vite MUST bake at build time. Without this the
# webapp falls back to http://localhost:3000 and hosted sign-in breaks. The
# negation must follow the **/.env.* rule to take effect.
!apps/webapp/.env.production
**/*.log
**/.DS_Store
# Rust / desktop / native build outputs not needed for server or web images.
apps/desktop/src-tauri/target
apps/*/build
